# Local development only.
#
# Deployed builds (Vercel) select their Supabase project automatically from the
# build environment — `main`/production uses the prod project and every preview
# branch (e.g. `develop`) uses the dev project. See src/lib/supabase.ts. You only
# need these variables to run the web app against a local Supabase stack or a
# custom backend; they are ignored by production and preview deployments.
#
# Local-stack values come from `supabase start` / `supabase status`.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:54321
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=replace-with-local-publishable-key
